<channel|>3. 養聲
廣東話：佢嚟緊要參加唱歌比賽，所以呢個禮拜要盡量少講嘢嚟養聲。
English: He is participating in a singing competition soon, so he needs to avoid talking as much as possible this week to preserve his voice.

4. 票尾
廣東話：入場之前記得留住張飛嘅票尾，出嚟嗰陣要用返佢嚟換錢。
English: Remember to keep the ticket stub before entering; you'll need it to get your money back when you leave.

5. hacker
廣東話：公司部伺服器被 hacker 攻破咗，所有客戶資料都流咗出去。
English: The company's server was breached by a hacker, and all customer data was leaked.

6. 石斛蘭
廣東話：呢種石斛蘭好特別，佢係依附喺樹幹上面生長嘅。
English: This kind of Dendrobium orchid is very special; it grows epiphytically on tree trunks.

7. 吊詭
廣東話：最吊詭嘅係，佢明明唔知件事，但竟然可以估中晒所有細節。
English: The paradoxical thing is that he clearly didn't know about the matter, yet he managed to guess every single detail correctly.

8. 吊詭
廣東話：個結局真係好吊詭，原本以為係開心結局，點知最後竟然係個悲劇。
English: The ending was truly absurd; I thought it would be a happy ending, but it turned out to be a tragedy.

9. 各為其主
廣東話：兩間公司雖然合作緊，但其實內部係各為其主，各有盤算。
English: Although the two companies are cooperating, internally they are each serving their own masters and have their own agendas.

10. 軨蓋
廣東話：今日係正式場合，你記得打條軨蓋，唔好著得太隨便。
English: Today is a formal occasion, so remember to wear a tie; don't dress too casually.

11. 打哥夫
廣東話：佢而家年紀大咗，最鍾意嘅消遣就係同班老友去打哥夫。
English: Now that he's older, his favorite pastime is playing golf with his old friends.

12. 免揀
廣東話：呢間舖頭啲貨係免揀嘅，老闆話全部一樣咁好，唔使揀。
English: The goods in this shop are non-selectable; the owner says they are all of the same quality, so there's no need to pick.

13. 擺闊佬
廣東話：佢雖然唔係好有錢，但每次出街都鍾意擺闊佬，請晒所有人食飯。
English: Although he isn't very wealthy, he likes to act like a big spender whenever he goes out, treating everyone to dinner.

14. 廣播劇
廣東話：我細個嗰陣好鍾意聽收音機入面播嘅廣播劇。
English: When I was young, I loved listening to radio dramas on the radio.

15. 錄影機
廣東話：以前啲人會用錄影機將電視節目錄低，方便之後再睇。
English: In the past, people used video recorders to record TV programs for later viewing.

16. 吟詩吟唔甩
廣東話：監視器錄到晒佢偷嘢嘅過程，佢而家證據確鑿，絕對吟詩吟唔甩。
English: The surveillance camera recorded the entire theft; with such concrete evidence, he absolutely cannot deny it.

17. 佈道大會
廣東話：個教會喺禮拜日舉辦咗一場大型佈道大會，吸引咗好多人參加。
English: The church held a large evangelistic meeting on Sunday, attracting many participants.

18. 寫手
廣東話：佢係一個專業嘅自由寫手，專門幫人寫專欄文章。
English: He is a professional freelance writer who specializes in writing column articles for others.

19. 寫手
廣東話：呢本小說其實係搵咗個寫手代筆，作者本人根本唔識寫書。
English: This novel was actually written by a ghostwriter; the author himself doesn't know how to write books at all.

20. 代打
廣東話：我今晚要加班，所以搵咗個代打幫我將個遊戲等級升上去。
English: I have to work overtime tonight, so I hired a booster to level up my game character for me.

21. 茶碗
廣東話：日本茶道入面，個茶碗嘅材質同形狀都好講究。
English: In the Japanese tea ceremony, the material and shape of the tea bowl are very meticulously considered.

22. 茶隔
廣東話：用茶隔沖茶就方便好多，唔使擔心啲茶葉會流晒入杯度。
English: Using a tea strainer makes brewing tea much more convenient, as you don't have to worry about the tea leaves flowing into the cup.

23. 只許州官放火，不准百姓點燈
廣東話：老闆自己遲到就話係開會，我遲到五分鐘就俾佢鬧，真係只許州官放火，不准百姓點燈。
English: The boss says he's late because of a meeting, but he scolds me for being five minutes late; it's a complete double standard.

24. 獨唱
廣東話：佢喺學校嘅音樂會上面表演獨唱，唱得非常之好。
English: She performed a solo at the school concert and sang beautifully.

25. 快人快事
廣東話：佢做嘢唔拖泥帶水，快人快事，大家都好鍾意同佢合作。
English: He works efficiently and gets things done quickly; everyone loves collaborating with him.

26. 四腳獸
廣東話：佢哋喺商場廁所入面做四腳獸，結果被保安發現而趕走。
English: They were engaging in sexual activity in the mall restroom and were caught and kicked out by security.

27. 無米粥
廣東話：兩間公司而家只係煲緊無米粥，具體嘅合作條款仲未傾好。
English: The two companies are currently only having preliminary discussions; the specific terms of cooperation have not yet been finalized.

28. 義會
廣東話：以前啲街坊好鍾意搞義會，互相幫忙借錢周轉。
English: In the past, neighbors loved organizing rotating credit associations to help each other with loans.

29. 榜文
廣東話：政府將新嘅法例寫成榜文貼喺街口，等所有市民都知道。
English: The government wrote the new regulations into a public notice and posted it at the street corner so all citizens would know.

30. MK名
廣東話：佢個社交媒體個名係「堅系唯愛小美」，典型嘅 MK名。
English: His social media handle is "Definitely Only Love Xiao Mei," a typical MK-style name. [end of text]


